content: Glad I found this a guy mentioned it a review for jumpgrid. I have it on iOS I don't have this game. Dissembler is a great game. I have no complaints. I came from my iphone to android bc I love the Pixel 4 XL. I bought this and will buy jumpgrid. I'll also buy a lot of this guy's games they are always top notch games for mobile. Thanks for making this awesome game. I plan on buy a lot of your games to help support the game making bc your games are great. Thanks!!!!!
it's annoying that when I open the game to check the daily puzzle, it goes straight to level 1 (after I finished the game) ,why wouldn't it start from the menu?
Very good logic game - makes you think hard to find the solutions
Very fun puzzle game with satisfying clicks. I thought the circle matching was hard to grasp but I'm just an idiot.
This game is amazing. It helps me deal with negative thoughts and anxiety. This app truly helps me. I can't explain how much it means to me. Thank you times a million

This is a really good game. Very simple yet so complex in the puzzles. I think it was well worth the price. I have played this, and enjoyed myself more than some free games. The asthetic reminds me of Monument Valley but more in depth on the puzzles. Totally worth it!
An ingenious puzzler that has super simple rules that are easy to understand, yet devilishly clever spatial challenges & surprising breadth.
An amazing and addictive puzzle game. A great brain jump starter.
Elegant and challenging!

AMAZING!! I absolutely love the audio; from the tinkering soundtrack, to the cranks and clicks of the turning puzzle pieces. Brilliantly done! Perfect game to simultaneously relax and challenge you. Highly recommended! ‚ù§Ô∏è

This is my favorite puzzler and has been since I got this game. It's simple to learn yet challenging to master. Also, 6 new daily puzzles every day (on top of the "campaign" mode and infinite mode) are why this is the only game that's a standalone icon on my phone and not buried in a folder with all the other games. Easily worth the asking price, and more.

The dailies are a very nice touch! I am finding that I use this game a 
couple of strategic times of the day if you take my meaning ;)

Dissembler is a surprisingly inventive puzzler. Rather than being designed 
for epiphany, the hook of the game is the interesting patterns and 
structures you solve. Gameplay consists of gaining the right perspective to 
tackle a level. The first few levels are a tour-de-force in doing this 
squeezing every possible idea out of the premise.
